        <abstract> 
<p>Struck by singular clarity of EH’s <hi rend="italic">Generelle Morphologie</hi>. Remarks on various authors seem too severe. Severity leads the reader to take the side of the attacked person.</p>  
<p>Making slow progress in correcting <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
